&lt;h2 id="local-image-note"&gt;
 Local image note
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For page bundles, put images beside &lt;code&gt;index.md&lt;/code&gt; and reference by filename only to get dimensions.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Mermaid and Math Demo</title><link>https://sothawang.github.io/posts/mermaid-and-math/</link><pubDate>Sun, 05 Oct 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://sothawang.github.io/posts/mermaid-and-math/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="mermaid"&gt;
